KUSIZE isangoma esishayele amaphoyisa ukuze kubanjwe obefunelwa icala lokubulala. UMnuz Sipho Mkhatshwa, ongumsolwa wokuqala ecaleni lokubulawa kukaHillary Gardee, waya esangomeni eyogeza ngemuva kokuba yena nabanye abasolwa bebulale le ntokazi. Umthombo osondelene nalolu daba utshele abeSowetan ukuthi uMkhatshwa wageqa amagula esebanjwe ngamaphoyisa, waze wakhipha nabanye ayebambisene nabo kulokhu. Lokhu kanye nezicathulo ezinegazi, ezitholakale endaweni ehlala abafundi, yikona okusize amaphoyisa ngaleli cala. Khonamanjalo iNyuvesi yaseMpumalanga ithumele incwadi komunye wabasolwa, uMnuz Philemon Lukhele, ethi ngeke isazisebenzisa izindawo zakhe ezihlala abafundi. ULukhele ungumnikazi wezindlu ezintathu ezaziwa ngeNsika Guest House, ezihlala abafundi bale nyuvesi. Kuthiwa kwasetshenziswa eyodwa yalezi zindlu ukugcina uGardee. Ngokwesitatimende, le nyuvesi ithi ayikwazi ukuqhubeka nokuhlalisa abafundi kule ndawo, ibeka ukuphepha kwabo phambili. Lokhu kulandela ukuvela kukaLukhele enkantolo ngoMeyi 10 (ngoLwesibili) ngamacala abucayi ahlanganisa nelokubulala. “Abafundi abahlala kulezi zindawo sebebikelwe ngokupheliswa kwenkontileka yenyuvesi nazo. Laba bafundi bazothuthelwa kwezinye izindawo,” kusho le nyuvesi ngesitatimende.